snippet.title: Howrse: the best virtual horse game!
snippet.description:
Join the adventure and play Howrse, the best virtual horse game for free!

Join a community of more than 12 million players and make new friends with the same passion as yours. 

Follow your dreams and start breeding your own horses, ponies or even unicorns.

Choose your horses among thousands, breed and improve their skills. Enjoy many great games to win equipements for your horses of for your equestrian center.

Alone or with friends to team up with, don't hesitate to join us, new players will always be welcomed and it is only a matter of time before you become the best breeder of the game!

🎵 Music
The Happy - Intropolis
-

💚 Thank you for watching! If you like our videos, don't forget to like them and to follow us.

🎮 P L A Y N O W
http://www.bit.ly/Play_Howrse_now

💌 S U P P O R T
